<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="aioseo-what-is-person-schema-markup">What is Person Schema Markup?</h2>



<p>Person schema markup is code you can apply to web pages about historical or contemporary people or fictional characters.</p>



<p>This code helps search engines understand your content better and that can improve your SEO.</p>



<p>In addition to person schema, there are dozens of schema types. For example, there’s schema markup available for recipes, events, courses, books, how-to content, FAQs, and much more.</p>



<p>To get started with person schema, we recommend you download the <a href="https://aioseo.com/pricing/">All-in-One (AIOSEO) plugin</a>.</p>



